== 联军干预之前的平民死亡数 ==
指3月17日以前，卡扎菲部队打死的平民数。

最保守的估计是1000人死亡<ref name="bbc.co.uk">{{cite news |author=Staff |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-12795971 |title=Libya: French Plane Fires on Military Vehicle |publisher=BBC News |date=19 March 2011 |accessdate=26 March 2011 |archive-date=2011-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110320125209/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-12795971 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；[[国际刑事法院|国际刑事法院]]于3月7日估计有1万人被杀<ref name="Irib">{{cite web|author=Staff|date=24 February 2011|url=http://english.irib.ir/news/political/item/71535-death-toll-in-libyan-popular-uprising-at-10000|title=Death Toll in Libyan Popular Uprising at 10,000|publisher=[[Islamic_Republic_of_Iran_Broadcasting|Islamic Republic of Iran Broadcasting]]|accessdate=26 March 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728152435/http://english.irib.ir/news/political/item/71535-death-toll-in-libyan-popular-uprising-at-10000|archivedate=2011年7月28日}}</ref>；3月2日，国际人权同盟估计3000人死亡；而[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]估计2000人被杀<ref name=RTnews.com>{{cite web|author=Staff|date=2 March 2011|url=http://rt.com/news/line/2011-03-02/|title=RT News Line, March 2|publisher=[[RT_(TV_network)|RT]]|accessdate=15 March 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110310042002/http://rt.com/news/line/2011-03-02/|archivedate=2011-03-10}}</ref>；同时，反对派宣称有6500人死亡<ref name=autogenerated3>{{Cite news|author=Staff|url=http://www.sify.com/news/at-least-3-000-dead-in-libya-rights-group-news-international-ldcxkhgggdh.html|title=At Least 3,000 Dead in Libya: Rights Group|publisher=[[Indo-Asian_News_Service|Indo-Asian News Service]] (via [[Sify_News|Sify News]])|date=2 March 2011|accessdate=18 March 2011|archive-date=2011-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812003947/http://www.sify.com/news/at-least-3-000-dead-in-libya-rights-group-news-international-ldcxkhgggdh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；利比亚人权联盟在3月5日估计有6000人被害<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news |author=Adams, Richard |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2011/mar/10/libya-uprising-gaddafi-live#block-15 |title=Libya Uprising – Thursday 10 March |work=The Guardian |date=10 March 2011 |accessdate=19 March 2011 |location=London |archive-date=2011-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110321150218/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/blog/2011/mar/10/libya-uprising-gaddafi-live#block-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated2" />。后来，部落发言人''Abdul Hafiz Ghoga''于3月20日报告说死亡人数达8000人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.net/live/africa/libya-live-blog-march-20-0 |title=Libya Live Blog – March 20 |publisher=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]] |date=March 20,  2011 |accessdate=March 20, 2011 |archive-date=2011-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430090611/http://blogs.aljazeera.net/live/africa/libya-live-blog-march-20-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

而截止2月22日，受伤人数估计达4000人。

