=== 死于反对派武装的人数 ===
已经有超过1700名卡扎菲军队和雇佣军被反对派打死<ref name="alleged_mercenaries">{{cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/black-men-mistaken-for-mercenaries-20110305-1biwb.html |title=Black men mistaken for mercenaries |publisher=www.smh.com.au |date=6 March 2011 |accessdate=19 June 2011 |archive-date=2011-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111117190559/http://www.smh.com.au/world/black-men-mistaken-for-mercenaries-20110305-1biwb.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。也有许多报道指出有不少卡扎菲军队是被政府军打死的。

2月18日，在班加西有2名警察被示威者吊死<ref name="xinhuanet1">{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-02/19/c_13739109.htm |title=Two policemen hanged in Libya protests |publisher=News.xinhuanet.com |date=19 February 2011 |accessdate=24 February 2011 |archive-date=2012-08-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AIbwbn7U?url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/world/2011-02/19/c_13739109.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，50名雇佣军（大多数来自[[乍得|乍得]]）在al-Baida被抗议者处决和烧死<ref name="massacres reported">{{cite news |author=Ian Black and Owen Bowcott |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/feb/18/libya-protests-massacres-reported |title=Libya protests: massacres reported as Gaddafi imposes news blackout | World news |publisher=The Guardian |date=18 February 2011 |accessdate=24 February 2011 |location=London |archive-date=2012-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121229021655/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/feb/18/libya-protests-massacres-reported |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中至少15人是在法院前面被处[[私刑|私刑]]死亡<ref name="Time-Foreign-Mercenaries">{{cite news |last=Hauslohner |first=Abigail |url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2053490,00.html |title=Libya's Alleged Foreign Mercenaries: More Gaddafi Victims? |publisher=TIME |date=23 February 2011 |accessdate=25 February 2011 |archive-date=2013-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130824010635/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2053490,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这些人的尸体被拍成视频以公示<ref>{{cite web |author=1:50 |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q6akmd6tfxg |title=African Mercenary Killed in Libya |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=24 February 2011 |archive-date=2015-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709162100/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q6akmd6tfxg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_s91AvXP2XQ&skipcontrinter=1 |title=African Mercenary Killed in Libya 2 |publisher=YouTube |date=22 February 2011 |accessdate=24 February 2011 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218184449/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_s91AvXP2XQ&skipcontrinter=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月23日，利政府证实有111名士兵死亡<ref>{{cite web |author=7:15 pm |url=http://www.asianage.com/international/libya-says-300-dead-violence-including-111-soldiers-193 |title=Libya says 300 dead in violence, including 111 soldiers |publisher=The Asian Age |date= |accessdate=24 February 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605040505/http://www.asianage.com/international/libya-says-300-dead-violence-including-111-soldiers-193 |archivedate=2011年6月5日 }}</ref>。

2月23日，一组22名政府军士兵武装尝试攻破Derna附近的一个空军基地，该地前几天被部落武装占领。数个小时后，22人都被俘虏，其中12人被枪决，1人被吊死<ref name="GlobeAndMail_110401">{{cite news | url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/africa-mideast/a-rebellion-divided-spectre-of-revenge-killings-hangs-over-eastern-libya/article1967949/page1/ | title=A rebellion divided: spectre of revenge killings hangs over eastern Libya | date=1 April 2011 | location=Toronto | work=The Globe and Mail | first=Graeme | last=Smith | accessdate=2011-11-21 | archive-date=2011-12-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230225113/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/africa-mideast/a-rebellion-divided-spectre-of-revenge-killings-hangs-over-eastern-libya/article1967949/page1/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2月15日到5月22日之间，37名前政府军在班加西被杀<ref name="newser.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.newser.com/article/d9nclre00/killings-of-gadhafi-agents-in-benghazi-raise-fears-of-reprisal-killings-in-rebel-held-libya.html|title=Killings of Gadhafi agents in Benghazi raise fears of reprisal killings in rebel-held Libya|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110619225912/http://www.newser.com/article/d9nclre00/killings-of-gadhafi-agents-in-benghazi-raise-fears-of-reprisal-killings-in-rebel-held-libya.html|archivedate=2011-06-19|accessdate=2011-11-21}}</ref>。

在[[米苏拉塔之战|米苏拉塔之战]]接近尾声时，至少27名来自[[马里|马里]]、[[尼日尔|尼日尔]]和[[乍得|乍得]]的雇佣军被处决<ref>[http://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/nationworld/sns-ap-ml-libya-pows,0,6257434.story?track=rss Libyan rebels hand out rules on POW treatment; some 300 in custody, including 10 foreigners]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

