4月1日，北约空袭[[布雷加|布雷加]]前线时，造成14个反政府部落武装成员死亡，7人受伤<ref>{{cite news |last=Meo |first=Nick |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8423675/Libya-Nato-warplanes-kill-14-rebels.html |title=Libya: Nato warplanes kill 14 rebels |publisher=Telegraph |date=2 April 2011 |accessdate=2011-04-04 |location=London |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405143058/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/libya/8423675/Libya-Nato-warplanes-kill-14-rebels.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4月7日，报道说在布雷加，北约炸死反政府部落武装10到13名，炸伤14到22名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jv_sNu4z2ePkq1HOS0P_x7-rgNdA?docId=CNG.6f1a3c295003e2f3af5b879590880652.321|title=NATO checking report of air strike on Libya rebels|publisher=[[Agence_France-Presse|AFP]]|date=2011-04-07|accessdate=2011-11-21|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606095232/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jv_sNu4z2ePkq1HOS0P_x7-rgNdA?docId=CNG.6f1a3c295003e2f3af5b879590880652.321|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

4月27日，一架北约战机在攻打米苏拉塔时，打死士兵12名，打伤5名<ref>{{cite news |last=Chivers |first=C.J. |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/28/world/africa/28libya.html?partner=rss&emc=rss |title=NATO Strike Kills 12 Libyan Rebels in Misurata |publisher=The New York times |date=27 April 2011 |accessdate=2011-04-28 |location=New York City |archive-date=2011-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430094056/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/28/world/africa/28libya.html?partner=rss&emc=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

